title: Cedar Walton 1991
description: Leigh interviews Cedar Walton when Cedar was in Minneapolis playing a club called Roxy's.  Leigh includes a few minutes of a live Cedar Walton trio performance recording of Off Minor by Thelonius Monk and also asks Cedar about his Monk interpretation and Monk's influence as well as some interesting observations of Italian audiences.
